*******************************
         Installation 
*******************************

	$ tar -xvf pair_reads.tgz 
	$ cd pair_reads
	$ make

*******************************
           Usage 
*******************************

	$ pairfa your_reads.fasta
	$ pairfq your_reads.fastq

*******************************
         	Output 
*******************************
  
Reads will be distributed among the following three files 
	
	your_reads_p1.fasta/q	:	Paired read #1
	your_reads_p2.fasta/q	:	Paired read #2
	your_reads_up.fasta/q	:	Unpaired reads


          



